        "::: {.figure-caption}\n",
        "The same experiments analyzed with and without a pre-treatment covariate. In this design, adjustment narrows the median confidence sequence (top) and raises the share of experiments that can stop by the planned end (bottom). Under the method's assumptions, both analyses have the same coefficient-wise asymptotic guarantee.\n",
